    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Cart] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0
) AS [c1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Quantity], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [c1].[Id] = [s].[CartId]

SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[CartId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[Quantity], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Cart] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0
) AS [c1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Quantity], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [c1].[Id] = [s].[CartId]
ORDER BY [c1].[Id], [s].[Id]

) AS [c1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Quantity], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [c0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [c1].[Id] = [s].[CartId]
ORDER BY [c1].[Id], [s].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

FROM [Order] AS [o]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]

        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AddressId], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalAmount], [o].[TransactionId], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[FullName], [a].[HouseName], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[LandMark], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[Pincode], [a].[Place], [a].[UserId], [s].[Id], [s].[OrderId], [s].[ProductId], [s].[ProductImage], [s].[ProductName], [s].[Quantity], [s].[TotalPrice], [s].[Id0], [s].[Brand], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Color], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Details], [s].[Image], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[ModifiedBy], [s].[ModifiedDate], [s].[OldPrice], [s].[Price], [s].[ProductName0], [s].[Seller], [s].[Stock]
FROM [Order] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [Address] AS [a] ON [o].[AddressId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductImage], [o0].[ProductName], [o0].[Quantity], [o0].[TotalPrice], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Brand], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Color], [p0].[CreatedBy], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Details], [p0].[Image], [p0].[IsDeleted], [p0].[ModifiedBy], [p0].[ModifiedDate], [p0].[OldPrice], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductName] AS [ProductName0], [p0].[Seller], [p0].[Stock]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Brand], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Color], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Details], [p].[Image], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[ModifiedDate], [p].[OldPrice], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductName], [p].[Seller], [p].[Stock]
        FROM [Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [o].[Id] = [s].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[Id], [a].[Id], [s].[Id]
